{"tid":2290031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Twitter：近期為30萬個帶選舉誤導信息帖文加上標籤 公眾希望他們這樣做","createTime":"2020-11-17T16:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T17:47:40.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"48bd8e541ff31f9749366660214acafd6fa46019","tid":2290031,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"Twitter：近期為30萬個帶選舉誤導信息帖文加上標籤<br />\n<br />\n美國社交媒體Twitter及Facebook的行政總裁，透過視像出席國會參議院司法委員會聽證會，就如何處理美國大選的不實資訊作證。Twitter行政總裁多爾西在書面證詞中表示，由上月27日至本月11期間，曾為30萬個帖文加上標籤，指內容有爭議或可能誤導，當中456條帖文加上警告信息，限制用戶分享。多爾西指，加上標籤是要限制危害選舉的信息散播，因為公眾希望他們這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n總統特朗普近期多段聲稱自己勝出大選，以及質疑多個州點票結果的帖文，都被Twitter加上標籤，指內容有爭議或與官方的消息不同。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2366717&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1WlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=e4294384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366717</a>"},{"pid":"e38fdfdac850c04340ce9f85977e9cd7d5cfe404","tid":2290031,"uid":171107,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohGyMWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohGyMWi.jpg&h=a840af02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb1e0ecc84b4a3507b522bff6836084170da59b8","tid":2290031,"uid":36134,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">因為公眾希望他們這樣做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁似曾相熟既感覺"},{"pid":"fb3ab5ae0ca715bfbed1101282f59a70731e1a0c","tid":2290031,"uid":251732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiiA0gE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiiA0gE.jpg&h=6de2266d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e5969ffde2ee0a4e205755ede2e543b0cc83eea","tid